(3689, 1, '2019-09-30 10:42:12', '2019-09-30 10:42:12', '<h3>What is BESDA</h3>		\n		<p>The BESDA Program Development Objective (PDO) is to increase equitable access for out-of-school children and improve literacy in focus states, and strengthen accountability for results, in basic education in Nigeria. The PDO mirrors the priorities of the UBE program, reaffirmed in the MSP focus on increasing access, improving quality, and strengthening the education system. Specifically, BESDA aims to support increases in access to basic education above and beyond natural population growth, so that out-of-school rates are reduced.</p>		\n										<img width=\"3840\" height=\"2160\" src=\"https://besda.app/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/zach-vessels-oOHBxlGADx4-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://besda.app/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/zach-vessels-oOHBxlGADx4-unsplash.jpg 3840w, https://besda.app/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/zach-vessels-oOHBxlGADx4-unsplash-600x338.jpg 600w, https://besda.app/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/zach-vessels-oOHBxlGADx4-unsplash-300x169.jpg 300w, https://besda.app/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/zach-vessels-oOHBxlGADx4-unsplash-768x432.jpg 768w, https://besda.app/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/zach-vessels-oOHBxlGADx4-unsplash-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3840px) 100vw, 3840px\" />											\n			<h4>Our Vision &amp; Mission</h4>		\n				<h3>\n					Vision Statement\n				</h3>\n								<p>Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet to change</p>\n				<h3>\n					Our Mission\n				</h3>\n								<p>Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet to change</p>', 'What is BESDA', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-is-besda', '', '', '2019-10-02 16:09:07', '2019-10-02 16:09:07', '', 0, 'https://besda.app/?page_id=3689', 0, 'page', '', 0),
